      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single crosshead displacement rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717. No variation in loading rate or temperature explored. This factor is below the required Gradation 3, representing a known gap. The shortfall is accepted given the quasi-static nature of the test and the dominance of geometric rather than rate-dependent effects in the QoI."
