      "rationale": "FEA fixture geometry modeled from ASTM F1717 standard drawings and verified against laboratory fixture photographs. UHMWPE block elastic modulus set to value measured from compression coupon test of the same block material. Pin and clevis geometry included explicitly. Equivalency between test and simulation inputs confirmed by side-by-side parameter table review."
